    IAsciiCommand, ICommandParameters, IAsciiCommandResponder, IAsciiResponse
    public class SleepCommand
extends AsciiSelfResponderCommandBase
implements ICommandParameters
    A command to send the reader to sleep as soon as it has responded to this command Note: this will disconnect the reader from the terminal
